Daemos received Gesper's message.

Daemos: Thank you for your report, Gesper. Can you ask if anyone 
volunteers to be the Autobot ambassador? Melchana should be back soon 
with the Hellgate, so she could pick up the ambassador at the Autobot 
ship.

Gesper: Roger.

At about the same time, Melchana arrived at the base.

Melchana: Tankor, get your ugly ass over here and start unloading the 
ship. Daemos, your freaking fruits could have blown me away in less 
than 1/1000 cycle if anyone had fired on me!

Tankor gets to the ship, Belthassan some steps behind him.

Tankor: Say one more thing against me and you are done for slag, 
Melchana!

Belthassan: Come and help us, sister. Daemos has another assignment 
for you after this is unloaded.

The three start getting the crates out of the Hellgate.
